name: SKOPE
notes:
Based on IntCal13 calibration curve. Hiatus of 2 yr set at 100 cm (European settlement horizon) to accomodate kink in accumulation rate.

Bacon command line:
Bacon('GLENMIRE',thick=5,hiatus.depths=100,hiatus.mean=2,acc.mean=c(1,20),d.max=380,depths.file=TRUE)

Bacon settings file:
0 #d.min
380 #d.max
1 #d.by
1 #depths.file
NA #slump
1 20 #acc.mean
1.5 1.5 #acc.shape
0.7 #mem.mean
4 #mem.strength
100 #hiatus.depths
2 #hiatus.mean
1 #hiatus.shape
0 #BCAD
1 #cc
0 #postbomb
IntCal13 #cc1
Marine13 #cc2
SHCal13 #cc3
ConstCal #cc4
cm #unit
0 #normal
3 #t.a
4 #t.b
0 #d.R
0 #d.STD
0.95 #prob
